# -*- mode:org -*-
#+TITLE: NuSMV notes

a repo to play around with [[nusmv.fbk.eu][NuSMV]].

* useful shell commands

- =go= :: initialize system

- =pick_state [-i interactively] [-r randomly]= :: pick initial state

- =simulate [-i interactively] [-k max number of steps]= :: simulate
     transitions

- =print_fair_transitions [-f format (dot, etc)] [-o output file]= :: print
     finite-state machine

* async processess
are apparently being deprecated, so should probably be avoided?
